@startuml
left to right direction
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1565C0
  FontSize 11
}

title UC-10: View Interactive Map

actor "User\n(A01/A02/A03)" as USER
actor "System Backend\n(A04)" as A04
actor "External Data Providers\n(A05)" as A05

rectangle "SmartLocateSG" {
  usecase "UC-10 View Interactive Map" as UC10

}

USER --> UC10
A04 --> UC10
A05 --> UC10



note right of UC10
Pre: Refer corresponding sequence precondition.
Flow: Main interaction follows sequence messages.
AC/EX: Alternate and exception branches traced from sequence.
end note

@enduml
